reviewText: Mike gives a very thorough breakdown and specific insturction for the ground wrestling game.  What seperates this from other "how to" videos is the genius of the chain set ups and the way Mike comes up with unexpected moves that work!

Extraordinarily thorough and complete compilation of all the critical chain wrestling moves. Great for both wrestlers and experienced MMA competitors. Very simple production and easy to understand explanations of the moves make this video a real stand out. Well done !
